{"tid":550970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男童坐的士遭針筒刺傷","createTime":"2018-02-05T08:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T09:51:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"84f99e9c78898e9eb06855dad2c274341a4169ed","tid":550970,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180205/20295474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F20295474&d=lcuFvZK4NcesZK%2FZ6r0c4QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c7f5ff8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F20295474&h=22e3f9a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180205/20295474</a><br />\n<br />\n男童坐的士遭針筒刺傷<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】一名6歲男童，昨午由父母帶同乘坐的士時，被一支遺留於後座罅隙之間的針筒刺傷右手指，男童父親懷疑有人惡意留下針筒，擔心愛兒從針頭感染惡菌，立即報警，男童事後送院檢查，警方撿走針筒進行化驗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180205/large/a0703a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180205%2Flarge%2Fa0703a.gif&h=6916789d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男童遭針筒（右圖）刺傷手指，事後送院檢查。黎家駒攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n父憂兒染惡菌<br />\n<br />\n昨午3時許，6歲姓黃男童由父母帶同在藍田平田邨截乘的士，往油塘一小學遞交入學申請表，男童坐後座，駛至油塘道23號對開街頭到達目的地時，一家三口下車，男童突「哇」的一聲，表示右手指頭刺痛，53歲父親查看後座坐位，赫見罅隙間有一支針筒，疑有人惡意遺留針筒在的士內大整蠱，擔心愛兒會經針口感染惡菌，於是報警。警方到場向65歲姓倪的士司機查問，案件交由觀塘警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n以往不時亦傳出有人惡意遺下針筒等尖刺物在巴士座椅上，最近一宗在上月底，有人在網上聲稱乘搭九巴81號線期間在座位上發現一排針灸針，不慎坐下會被刺入身體，但九巴回應經檢查同線巴士後，未有發現任何相關危險品。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎家駒"},{"pid":"1b9505531bb9c85728111e86c8727272c6f66992","tid":550970,"uid":118623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"咁就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43b5fac353ecc25db646a588f64d5f8f64c03a8","tid":550970,"uid":125061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"閪都未屌就中愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a57b765184eada827bd297da37cfd520d8f0027","tid":550970,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"真係會嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d7b5a514b44e00739d01901fdaaee10af60c57","tid":550970,"uid":20337,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4093/4944393242_77fdde80d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.static.flickr.com%2F4093%2F4944393242_77fdde80d7.jpg&h=6cd56106&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aedded0cb6014373f6548681d94b442dc5006c09","tid":550970,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f43b5fac353ecc25db646a588f64d5f8f64c03a8","tid":550970,"uid":125061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"閪都未屌就中愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:55:21.000Z","msg":"中左愛滋再屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e037245ddbd38614ad0959797680fed90149ce53","tid":550970,"uid":10726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"wa diu,<br />\n即刻諗到戲院啲坐位"},{"pid":"a506f13e25c7e7b46bf2543b074d6e0625b6ef78","tid":550970,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828ddde1837987c51de263f806c6029fb850aad2","ti